      <title>欧盟与南美贸易协定为何终将达成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/eu-mercosur-trade-deal-what-does-the-europe-south-america-agreement-involve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟和南美国家花了超过四分之一世纪的时间试图达成自由贸易协议。今年，随着世界最大贸易伙伴——美国和中国——之间即将爆发的贸易战，谈判变得更加紧迫，这促使其他地区寻求新的商业伙伴关系以减轻打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/eu-mercosur-trade-deal-what-does-the-europe-south-america-agreement-involve</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 07:30:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿德法鲁霍：尼日利亚通胀斗争尚未结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/adefalujo-nigeria-inflation-fight-not-over-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚 11 月份通胀率高于预期，年通胀率已达到 34.6%。该国央行预计将加息延续到明年。Meristem Nigeria 投资研究分析师 Matilda Adefalujo 告诉彭博社首席非洲通讯员 Jennifer Zabasajja，高油价和汇率将继续影响该国，尤其是在假期期间。
（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/adefalujo-nigeria-inflation-fight-not-over-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 07:19:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行决策前，英国通胀率跃升至八个月高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/uk-inflation-jumps-to-eight-month-high-ahead-of-boe-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国11月份通胀率升至八个月高位，进一步高于英国央行2%的目标，并支持市场预期该央行将在今年最后一次会议上维持利率不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/uk-inflation-jumps-to-eight-month-high-ahead-of-boe-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 07:04:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国维持基准利率不变，警告不确定性加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/thailand-holds-key-rate-to-stay-neutral-despite-rate-cut-calls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行在十月份意外下调基准利率后，维持其基准利率不变，警告称，由于拒绝政府进一步放松政策的要求，未来的不确定性将会增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/thailand-holds-key-rate-to-stay-neutral-despite-rate-cut-calls</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 07:01:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
